DESCRIPTION:Speaker: Dr. Inga Ulusoy\, Dr. Harald Mack\, Generative AI is emerging as a major creative force that supports humans in content creation.  AI coding tools can support software development on many levels. In this short course\, participants will get started with using GitHub copilot in VSCode as effective coding tools\nHost: Scientific Software Center\nVenue: Mathematikon Bauteil A\, Im Neuenheimer Feld 205\, conference room 5/104\nLink: https://www.ssc.uni-heidelberg.de/en/getting-started-with-generative-ai-coding-tools\nDuration: 1h 30m
